name: QUICKIE003 (bed knife)
description:
An original Gory Orgy mini-loop. 3 seconds. 1228X1228, H264, 2021
QUICKIE003 is a multi-layered animation that utilises more than one machine-learning model. A hostile, shape-shifting mass (AI-generated erotica) is conspicuously analysed by a machine-learning model that identifies people and objects. QUICKIE003 is one of 25. One copy is retained by the artist, while the other 24 are available for purchase. Gory Orgy is the experimental machine-learning project by kiwi artist and film-maker Ed Lust.
